1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,769
A local Agent can observe what someone clicks.

2
00:00:03,769 --> 00:00:11,107
It cannot reliably infer why a step matters, which exception applies, or what must never happen.

3
00:00:11,107 --> 00:00:19,362
Radeon Voice Skill Foundry captures that missing intent through a private spoken procedure and an aligned action trace.

4
00:00:19,362 --> 00:00:28,076
It produces a governed Agent Skill with typed rules, minimum permissions, adversarial tests, receipts, and a hash-bound proof package.

5
00:00:28,276 --> 00:00:40,466
The final validation ran on an AMD Radeon Pro W7900-class allocation: GFX eleven hundred, about forty-eight gigabytes of VRAM, and rock-em 7.2.1.

6
00:00:40,466 --> 00:00:43,791
Kwen three ASR handled speech recognition.

7
00:00:43,791 --> 00:00:49,332
Kwen three, four-B Instruct compiled the procedure into structured constraints.

8
00:00:49,332 --> 00:00:57,644
On public commit c759a41, all twenty-one tests and the production build passed inside Radeon Cloud.

9
00:00:57,844 --> 00:01:20,035
The spoken procedure defines the hidden rules of a private project review: keep only P-zero and P-one findings, remove salary data, draft email but never send automatically, ask for confirmation when an owner is missing, and create a calendar hold only when a due date exists.

10
00:01:20,035 --> 00:01:28,237
Before those words become policy, the Voice Evidence Gate measures level, clipping, silence, format, and source integrity.

11
00:01:28,237 --> 00:01:34,508
It also binds the original transcript hash, so later edits require explicit review.

12
00:01:34,708 --> 00:01:42,584
The Agent retrieves local policy evidence and combines it with the transcript and action trace.

13
00:01:42,584 --> 00:01:53,610
Kwen three, four-B produced thirteen constraints in 24.13 seconds, with 368 milliseconds time to first token and 20.07 tokens per second.

14
00:01:53,610 --> 00:01:59,911
Deterministic guardrails preserve critical Chinese semantics even when the model misses them.

15
00:01:59,911 --> 00:02:03,061
Salary data becomes a redaction rule.

16
00:02:03,061 --> 00:02:06,737
A missing owner becomes a confirmation rule.

17
00:02:06,737 --> 00:02:10,412
The due-date clause remains an only-if condition.

18
00:02:10,612 --> 00:02:16,383
Verification proves the voice evidence first, then executes unsafe paths before promotion.

19
00:02:16,383 --> 00:02:30,810
The final Radeon run passed all seven fixtures: salary data was removed, out-of-scope findings were skipped, missing context opened review, automatic sending was blocked, and unapproved network writes were denied.

20
00:02:30,810 --> 00:02:37,062
We also modified the client payload to claim that mail sending was allowed.

21
00:02:37,062 --> 00:02:44,756
The server ignored the untrusted fields, resolved the authoritative run, and kept mail dot send denied.

22
00:02:44,956 --> 00:02:56,214
The package contains a GAIA-compatible skill definition, least-privilege policy, fixtures, receipts, retrieved evidence, source-bound voice evidence, and the proof bundle.

23
00:02:56,214 --> 00:02:58,466
Raw audio is excluded.

24
00:02:58,466 --> 00:03:06,910
A verified skill can be versioned in local procedural memory and reused without model generation.

25
00:03:06,910 --> 00:03:14,791
Compact output reduced median tokens by 29.42 percent and generation latency by 30.03 percent.

26
00:03:14,791 --> 00:03:20,420
Exact verified-skill reuse measured 2.18 milliseconds median HTTP round trip.

27
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:26,195
Radeon Voice Skill Foundry turns local voice interaction into capability creation.

28
00:03:26,195 --> 00:03:28,223
Actions capture what happened.

29
00:03:28,223 --> 00:03:33,291
Voice captures why, when, exceptions, and what must never happen.

30
00:03:33,291 --> 00:03:45,963
The final proof scored one hundred out of one hundred for source quality, passed seven out of seven fixtures, and preserved mail sending as denied.

31
00:03:45,963 --> 00:03:47,483
Speak the SOP.

32
00:03:47,483 --> 00:03:49,004
Prove the Skill.
